title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2007-12 Altima 4-Door Sedan LED Fog Lights
description:
This video is designed to guide you through the installation process of a set of Spyder Auto LED Fog Lights (though the principles of installation are the same regardless of fog light type) on a Nissan Altima 4-Door Sedan.

Does not fit 2010-12 Altima "S" models
tags: Spyder LED Fog Lights, Nissan Altima, how to install, spyder lights
